attributes.title: Awful
attributes.review:
I got this app as a middle school librarian in order to keep track of the snakes in my car, and let me say, this app did NOT deliver. I ended up finding the carcass of an Aztec prince in the backseat, an undersized peach that was barely hotter than room temperature kept in the dashboard, a gnome shoved into the headrest of the passenger seat, and the tailgate was kept forced open by a magical barrier which led homeless men to seek refuge in my trunk. This app is CURSED. 
Installing this app also caused me to get a virus on my phone despite the vpn that I use. I would get a call every seven minutes flat that would only say, "It's the Chinese Virus because it comes from China." I really do not appreciate the racist statements this app has filled my minutes with. I am unable to decline the messages as well. 
All in all, worst installment In have ever made.
